extends ../layouts/base-whitefooter.jade

block head
  title Install | DC/OS
  meta(property='og:locale', content='en_US')
  meta(property='og:type', content='article')
  meta(property='og:title', content='Install | DC/OS')
  meta(property='og:image', content='https://dcos.io/assets/images/social-img.png')
  meta(property='og:description', content='Install the latest version of DC/OS locally, on-premises, or in the cloud, and find resources for beginners.')
  meta(property='og:url', content='https://dcos.io/')
  meta(property='og:site_name', content='DC/OS')
  meta(name='twitter:card', content='summary')
  meta(name='twitter:site', content='@dcos')
  meta(name='twitter:title', content='Install | DC/OS')
  meta(name='twitter:card', content='summary_large_image')
  meta(name='twitter:image', content='https://dcos.io/assets/images/social-img.png')
  meta(name='twitter:description', content='Install the latest version of DC/OS locally, on-premises, or in the cloud, and find resources for beginners.')

block content

  .container.container--dark-background.pb1.px2.sm-pb0(style='display: block;')
    .mx-auto.max-width-4
      +header(style='padding: 0;')

    .mx-auto.max-width-4
      .container__content.community-hero
        h1.mb0 Install



  //- Install methods
  .outer-container.clearfix.py4.px2#install
    .row
      .max-width-4.mx-auto
        .mxn2.flex.flex-auto.flex-wrap.items-center
          .lg-col-8.col-12.xs-col-12.px2.mx-auto
            h2.pb2.sm-center.mx-auto Choose a provider and install DC/OS
            p.sm-center.mx-auto.pb4 Installation involves configuring your infrastructure and installing DC/OS bits on top. Some install methods will configure your infrastructure for you, which results in limited functionality or control. Use the advanced install for production clusters.

        .mxn2.flex.flex-auto.flex-wrap.flex-start

          div.lg-col-4.col-6.xs-col-12.xs-center.px3.py3.center.card.bg-gray.relative(style="justify-content: inherit; padding-bottom: 2.45rem")
            img.hero-list__item__image(src="/assets/images/icons/local.svg")
            h4 Development
            p.hero-list__item__copy__paragraph.small(style='min-height: 7rem;')
              |Try DC/OS by installing a dcos-vagrant cluster on your local machine. Room for workloads is limited by CPU and memory. (limited functionality)
            .flex.flex-end.mt-auto(style='width: 100%')
            a(href='https://github.com/dcos/dcos-vagrant', style='width: 100%;').btn.btn-primary.center.m0 Local installation

          div.lg-col-4.col-6.xs-col-12.xs-center.px3.py3.center.card.bg-gray.relative(style="justify-content: inherit; padding-bottom: 2.45rem")
            img.hero-list__item__image(src="/assets/images/icons/cloud.svg")
            h4 Proof of Concept
            p.hero-list__item__copy__paragraph.small(style='min-height: 7rem;')
              | Deploy DC/OS using public cloud templates, for fast demos and POCs. Install DC/OS with a few clicks or commands. (limited functionality)
            a(href='https://docs.mesosphere.com/latest/installing/oss/cloud/' style='color: #7D58FF') Documentation
            .flex.flex-end.mt-auto(style='width: 100%')
              div.dropdown.z-500(style='text-align: left; left: 0; width: 100%; position: relative;')
                a.btn.btn-primary.mb0.block.center.no-arrow.text-white.bg-heliotrope Cloud templates
                  img.ml1.align-middle(src='/assets/images/icons/arrow-down-docs-unselected-white.svg' style='margin-top: -2px;')
                ul
                  li: a(href='https://downloads.dcos.io/dcos/stable/aws.html', target='_blank') Amazon Web Services
                  li: a(href='https://downloads.dcos.io/dcos/stable/azure.html', target='_blank') Azure
                  li: a(href='https://docs.mesosphere.com/latest/installing/oss/cloud/gce/', target='_blank') Google Cloud Platform

          div.lg-col-4.col-6.xs-col-12.xs-center.px3.py3.center.card.bg-gray.relative(style="justify-content: inherit; padding-bottom: 2.45rem")
            img.hero-list__item__image(src="/assets/images/icons/on-premesis.svg")
            h4 Production
            p.hero-list__item__copy__paragraph.small(style='min-height: 7rem;')
              | Follow the advanced installation instructions to create production ready DC/OS clusters on any infrastructure. (full functionality)
            a(href='https://docs.mesosphere.com/latest/installing/oss/custom/advanced/' style='color: #7D58FF') Documentation
            .flex.flex-end.mt-auto(style='width: 100%')
              a(href='https://downloads.dcos.io/dcos/stable/dcos_generate_config.sh', style='width: 100%;').btn.btn-primary.center.m0 Download DC/OS

  //- 101 Tutorial

  .outer-container.bg-gray.clearfix.py4.px2
    .row
      .max-width-4.mx-auto
        .mxn2.flex.flex-auto.flex-wrap.center
          .lg-col-8.col-12.xs-col-12.px2.mx-auto.pb2.center
            h2 DC/OS 101 tutorial
            p If you already have DC/OS installed on your cluster and aren't sure what to do next, try walking through the 101 tutorial, which is designed to give you hands-on experience with the essential pieces of DC/OS right away. Follow the simple recipes, or read and try the "deep dives" to learn how DC/OS works behind the scenes.

        .flex.flex-auto.flex-wrap.lg-col-8.col-12.xs-col-12.mx-auto.pb2
          h4(style='max-width: inherit;') The DC/OS 101 tutorial covers the following topics:
          .lg-col-6.col-6.xs-col-12.xs-center.px2.pb3
            ul.inherit-ul.left-align
              li Installing services
              li Deploying apps (containerized and non-containerized)
              li Connecting multiple applications
              li Service discovery

          .lg-col-6.col-6.xs-col-12.xs-center.px2.pb3
            ul.inherit-ul.left-align
              li Load-balancing (within the cluster and externally)
              li Making applications accessible from outside the cluster
              li Investigating/debugging common problems

          .col-12.px2.pt2.center
            a(href='https://docs.mesosphere.com/latest/tutorials/dcos-101/', style='width: 100%;').btn.btn-primary Start the 101 Tutorial

  //- Kubernetes
  .outer-container.bg-white.clearfix.pt2.pb4.px2
    .row
      .max-width-4.mx-auto
        .mxn2.flex.flex-auto.flex-wrap
          .lg-col-8.col-12.xs-col-12.px2.mx-auto.center(style='padding-top: 2rem;')
            h2 Kubernetes on DC/OS
            p DC/OS automates the steps to install and maintain a highly available Kubernetes cluster, and allows you to run it alongside other workloads. Once you have a DC/OS cluster up and running, try spinning up a Kubernetes cluster.
          .col-12.px2.pt2.center
            a(href='https://github.com/mesosphere/dcos-kubernetes-quickstart', style='width: 100%;').btn.btn-primary Quick Start Guide



  //- Additional resources
  .outer-container.bg-gray.clearfix.pt2.pb4.px2
    .row
      .max-width-4.mx-auto
        .mxn2.flex.flex-auto.flex-wrap
          h2.pb4.center.mx-auto Additional resources for beginners

      .max-width-4.mx-auto.pb4
        .mxn2.flex.flex-auto.flex-wrap
          a.card.col-4.left-align.px3.py3.bg-white(style='display: block' href='https://docs.mesosphere.com/latest/overview/')
            h4 Documentation
            p.mb2.mt0 Read the documentation's overview of DC/OS for a conceptual description of DC/OS's inner workings.
            span(style='color: #7D58FF') Read the docs

          a.card.col-4.left-align.px3.py3.bg-white(style='display: block' href='/community')
            h4 Community
            p.mb2.mt0 Get help via mailing list, Slack, or Stack Overflow by joining the DC/OS community.
            span(style='color: #7D58FF') Join the community

          a.card.col-4.left-align.px3.py3.bg-white(style='display: block' href='https://docs.mesosphere.com/latest/tutorials/')
             h4 Tutorials
             p.mb2.mt0 Tutorials are hands-on walkthroughs of DC/OS with explanations.
             span(style='color: #7D58FF') Try a tutorial


  //- Footer
  .container
    +footer
